    Radius
    Linear method to calculate intersection of circle and center of circle to a touch.
    RadiusDemoActivity
    Demonstrates a very simple and efficient linear algebraic method of finding the intersection of a ray (to a touch point) and a circle drawn on a map using the google maps api for android.
